section.ftco-section
  .container
    .row.align-items-center
      .col-md-6.pr-md-5
        .heading-section.text-md-right.ftco-animate
          span.subheading Discover
          h2.mb-4 Our Product
          p.mb-4
            | Every coffee we sell has gone through sorting and grading processes beforehand, reducing the risk of defects and poor quality in our products. 
            | If a product is received with damage caused by production (not by shipping or buyer error), a report can be submitted within 24 hours, accompanied by proof of transaction and shipping receipt.
